---
// Industry Accreditations Section Component
---

<section class='industry-accreditations py-5'>
  <div class='container py-4'>
    <!-- Mobile View (d-block d-lg-none) -->
    <div class='d-block d-lg-none'>
      <h2 class='fw-bold mb-3'>Industry Accreditations</h2>

      <p class='mb-5'>
        Accreditations for our Land Specialists assures our land buyers and
        sellers that they're working with the most knowledgeable, dedicated and
        qualified agents available
      </p>

      <!-- Mobile Accreditation Items - Stacked -->
      <div class='d-flex flex-column align-items-center mb-4'>
        <img
          src='/images/certifications/nda-logo.png'
          alt='National Deer Association'
          class='certification-logo mb-3'
          width='150'
        />
        <p class='fw-bold text-center mb-5'>NDA Deer Steward Level I</p>
      </div>

      <div class='d-flex flex-column align-items-center mb-4'>
        <img
          src='/images/certifications/alc-logo.png'
          alt='Accredited Land Consultant'
          class='certification-logo mb-3'
          width='150'
        />
        <p class='fw-bold text-center mb-5'>Accredited Land Consultant</p>
      </div>

      <div class='d-flex flex-column align-items-center mb-4'>
        <img
          src='/images/certifications/faa-logo.png'
          alt='FAA Certification'
          class='certification-logo mb-3'
          width='150'
        />
        <p class='fw-bold text-center mb-5'>
          FAA Part 107 Remote Pilot Certification
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class='d-flex flex-column align-items-center mb-4'>
        <img
          src='/images/certifications/wpcls-logo.png'
          alt='Whitetail Properties Certified Land Specialist'
          class='certification-logo mb-3'
          width='150'
        />
        <p class='fw-bold text-center mb-5'>
          Whitetail Properties Certified Land Specialist
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Desktop View (d-none d-lg-block) -->
    <div class='d-none d-lg-block'>
      <h2 class='text-center display-5 fw-bold mb-4'>
        INDUSTRY LEADING ACCREDITATIONS
      </h2>

      <p class='text-center mb-5 px-5 mw-75 mx-auto'>
        Our commitment to putting your needs above everything is supported by
        our dedication to being the most educated and qualified Land Specialists
        with the deepest understanding of the land market. We're ready to show
        you why we are the trusted choice for helping sellers reach their goals
        quickly and maximizing their property's value.
      </p>

      <!-- Desktop Accreditation Items - Row -->
      <div
        class='row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-3 row-cols-lg-5 g-4 justify-content-center mt-5'
      >
        <!-- NDA Level I -->
        <div class='col text-center'>
          <img
            src='/images/certifications/nda-logo.png'
            alt='National Deer Association'
            class='certification-logo mb-3'
            width='120'
          />
          <p class='fw-bold'>NDA Deer Steward Level I</p>
        </div>

        <!-- NDA Level II -->
        <div class='col text-center'>
          <img
            src='/images/certifications/nda-logo.png'
            alt='National Deer Association'
            class='certification-logo mb-3'
            width='120'
          />
          <p class='fw-bold'>NDA Deer Steward Level II</p>
        </div>

        <!-- ALC -->
        <div class='col text-center'>
          <img
            src='/images/certifications/alc-logo.png'
            alt='Accredited Land Consultant'
            class='certification-logo mb-3'
            width='120'
          />
          <p class='fw-bold'>Accredited Land Consultant</p>
        </div>

        <!-- WP Certified -->
        <div class='col text-center'>
          <img
            src='/images/certifications/wpcls-logo.png'
            alt='Whitetail Properties Certified Land Specialist'
            class='certification-logo mb-3'
            width='120'
          />
          <p class='fw-bold'>Whitetail Properties Certified Land Specialist</p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAA -->
        <div class='col text-center'>
          <img
            src='/images/certifications/faa-logo.png'
            alt='FAA Certification'
            class='certification-logo mb-3'
            width='120'
          />
          <p class='fw-bold'>FAA Part 107 Remote Pilot Certification</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .industry-accreditations {
    background-color: #f8f9fa;
    background-image: url("https://lightsail.wpsitestage.dev/build/assets/background-topography-top-left-Bq41VDsp.svg"),
      url("https://lightsail.wpsitestage.dev/build/assets/background-topography-bottom-right-fz0-uggA.svg");
    background-position:
      top left,
      bottom right;
    background-repeat: no-repeat, no-repeat;
    background-size:
      40% auto,
      40% auto;
  }

  .certification-logo {
    height: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  /* Center the main paragraph on desktop */
  .mw-75 {
    max-width: 75%;
  }
</style>
